Hukumar ta fi son kiran 'yan majalisar wakilai na majalisar dokokin Wales ko kuma 'WMP', amma shawarar 'MWP' ta samu goyon baya sosai a cikin shawarwarin jama'a.
'Yan majalisar suna iya ba da shawarar wasu hanyoyin, amma gwagwarmayar samun yarjejeniya na iya zama ciwon kai ga shugaban kasa, Elin Jones, wanda ke shirye ya gabatar da kudurin gyare-gyare a cikin mako guda.
