LeBron zai fara wasa da San Diego Lakers ranar Lahadi
Magoya bayan kungiyar sun yi fatan ganin LeBron James ya fara wasa a Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton James ya sanar da cewa zai buga wasa da Denver Nuggets a San Diego ranar Lahadi.
Amma ba mu riga mun yanke shawarar tsawon lokacin da za mu yi wasa ba.
"Ya fi daya, amma kasa da minti 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Sakataren Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasa na dan lokaci.
Bayan atisayen wannan makon, an tambayi James game da shirin Lakers na lashe wasanni shida na kakar wasan farko.
"Ba na bukatar wasanni na kakar wasa don in kasance a shirye a matsayin da nake a yanzu".
Trump ya yi yakin neman zabe a West Virginia, YouTube Channel
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara yakin neman zabe a wannan daren a garin Wheeling, na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin jerin 'yan takara biyar na farko da Trump zai gabatar a mako mai zuwa, wanda zai kara da cewa zai tsaya a wurare masu kusa da shi, Tennessee da Mississippi.
An dage zaben na zaben a kotun koli, kuma Trump na son ya goyi bayan zaben na watanni shida da za a yi a watan Nuwamba mai zuwa, saboda jam'iyyar Republican na iya rasa rinjaye a majalisa.
A wane lokaci ne za a fara yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia a yau kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
An shirya jawabin Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, don Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, a karfe bakwai na yamma, lokacin Kudu.
Za ku iya kallon yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia a yanzu a kan YouTube.
Trump zai iya magana game da sauraron da za a yi a Kotun Koli a wannan makon game da nadin Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka dage na mako guda, har sai an kammala binciken FBI kan karar fyade.
Amma babban dalilin irin wannan kamfen shine don taimakawa jam'iyyar Republican ta samu dan kadan daga cikin rinjaye a zaben na Nuwamba.
Kamfen din Trump na da kwarin gwiwa kan masu neman zabe da magoya bayan su da ke son gudanar da zabuka biyar a mako mai zuwa, yayin da jam'iyyar Republican ke kokarin fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Yawancin majalisar dokoki na da muhimmanci ga shugaban kasa, don haka zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama, saboda akwai wani lokaci mai wuya a gabanmu", in ji sakataren yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa ga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
Taron na yau a filin wasa na Wesbanko a Wheeling zai iya jawo masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma zai iya jawo hankalin Pittsburgh a labarai, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump ya kai ziyara karo na biyu a West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da aka kada.
Trump yana neman taimakon dan takararsa na Republican a majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya yi kasafi.
"Babu wata alama mai kyau ga Mauritius cewa shugaban kasa zai zo ya taimaka", in ji Simon Heather, masanin kimiyya a jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA na shirin yin yaki a ranar Lahadi
