Turai ta ci Ryder Cup da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe
A ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder ta Turai, kungiyar ta samu nasara ta 10-6 a kan Amurka a wasan golf na kwallaye hudu da biyu a ranar Asabar.
Dakarun Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci Tiger Woods da nasara biyu, nasara ta maki hudu a La Golf Nacional.
Thomas Bjorn, a gefen Turai, ya yi ƙoƙari ya dawo da abin da ya rasa a Hazelton shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya ci Amurkawa da ƙwallo huɗu da suka fi ƙarfinsa, kuma ya kammala da ci 3-1.
A wasan golf biyu ko biyu, Amurka ta ba da babbar nasara, ta ci biyu, amma ba ta iya cin nasara ba.
Jim Furyk yana bukatar maki takwas a wasanni 12 da ya buga a ranar Lahadi don kada ya ci nasara.
Fleetwood shine dan Turai na farko da ya ci kwallaye hudu a jere, tare da Molinari, "Mollywood" sun zama biyu na biyu a tarihin Ryder Cup da suka ci kwallaye hudu a wasanninsu na farko.
Woods da Patrick Reed sun ci Woods da dan wasan Amurka Bryson Deschambon da ci 5-4
