Yanzu shafi daya daga cikin kalandarmu: Shekaru 136 da suka wuce, a ranar 30 ga watan Satumba, 1982 - a wannan rana ne aka haifi wani masanin kimiyyar lissafi na nan gaba Johann Wilhelm Hans Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro hanyar da za ta iya nunawa da kuma auna radiyo, kuma wannan ya kai ga gina na'urar lissafin Geiger, wanda aka fi sani da shi.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, lissafin Geiger ya zama tushen al'adun pop kamar yadda masanin kimiyya-cowboy Roy Rogers da Dale Evans suka yi a cikin fim din "The Bell of the Coronation " na 1950:
Mutum: "To, daga ina wannan ya fito?"
Rogers: "Wannan shi ne na'urar lissafin Giger da muke amfani da ita wajen nuna ma'adanai masu aiki da hasken wuta kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin atom a cikin ma'adinai".
Evans ya ce, "Ya na shirin harbe ni, ku gaya mini!"
