Girgizar ƙasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ya afkawa birnin Palo, a ƙasar Indonesia, a ranar Jumma'a, ya kashe mutane fiye da 384, kuma adadin waɗanda suka mutu yana ƙaruwa.
Ba a samu sakonni daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin Palu, inda girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta fi kusa da inda ta auku.
An kwashe mutane 16,000 bayan bala'in da ya auku a Palau.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da yankin Palau da Donggala da ke tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke cikin tafki a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma yana da yawan jama'a kimanin mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da haihuwar.
Donggala  Regent wanda ke da nisan mil 180 (300 km) a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin shekara ta 2017, mazaunan yankin suna da yawan mutane 299,200.
Kamun kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin yankin na Tsakiyar Sulawesi da musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Akwai ma'adinai da yawa na nickel a lardin, amma mafi girma a Morava, a gefen teku na Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi ta damun Paul da Donggala da tsunami sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami da ya auku a yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996 ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific mai yawan girgizar kasa kuma tana fuskantar girgizar kasa a kai a kai.
Waɗannan su ne manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na shekarun baya bayan nan:
Ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, 2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a arewacin Sumatra a gabar yammacin yankin Aceh, Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami a kasashe 14 inda mutane 226,000 suka mutu a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su mazauna Aceh ne.
2005: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
A tsibirin Nias da ke Sumatra, ɗarurruwan mutane suka mutu.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin ƙarfin 6.8 ta afkawa kudu maso gabashin tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami a gaɓar tekun kudu, wanda ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin yammacin Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 aka kashe.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta kai ga tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 a tsibirin Mentawai, a Sumatra, ta halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ta kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai tsanani ta lalata yankin Pidi-Jai na Aceh, kuma mutane sun firgita saboda mummunan girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami ba, amma sama da mutane 100 sun mutu a halaka gine-gine.
