Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na son a yi amfani da hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wanda ake zargi da aikata ta'addanci a birnin New York
Ofishin kotun tarayya na birnin New York na son a yi amfani da hukuncin kisa na musamman, wanda ba a taba amfani da shi ba tun 1953, a kan mai zargin kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York, Saifullo Saipow, wanda ya kashe mutane takwas.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi hayar mota mai kama da mota a watan Oktoba, inda ya shirya kai hari a kan hanyar keke a yankin West na Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke barazana.
A cewar rahoton da aka bayar na hukuncin kisa a yankin kudancin New York, don a zartar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipowa ta kashe mutane takwas "da gangan" kuma ta yi musu rauni "da gangan".
Bisa ga takardun kotu, ya kamata a yanke masa hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta yanke hukuncin da ya zargi Saipov da laifuffuka 22 da suka hada da zargin aikata laifuka masu tsari, cin hanci da rashawa da kuma kashe mutane takwas da niyyar ta'addanci, wanda ya saba amfani da shi a matsayin tuhuma ta babban mai gabatar da kara na tarayya.
A cewar mai gabatar da kara, harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da shiri sosai", inda ya bayyana ayyukan Saipov a matsayin "abin ƙyama, na zalunci da lalata".
"Saifullo Habibullayevich Saipov ya yi rauni sosai kuma ya kashe Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Anne-Laura Decatt, Darren Drake, Ariel Early, Ernan Ferrucci, Ernan Diego Mendoz da Alejandro Damian Pagnuckos, dangi da abokai", in ji sanarwar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma ke nan da aka kashe mutum na ƙarshe a yankin Kudu na New York.
An zargi wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da kisan dillalan miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009.
A shekarar 1953, shekaru biyu kafin wannan, an yanke wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a birnin New York saboda alkawarin yin leken asiri a lokacin yakin sanyi da Tarayyar Soviet.
An kashe su biyu a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, dan kasar Uzbekistan Saipov bai yi nadama ba game da abin da ya yi, ko da yake kwanaki da watanni sun shude bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce mutumin ya ce bai yi nadama ba.
A cewar hukuncin, bidiyon ISIS da ke wayar Saipov ne ya karfafa wannan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya kuma nemi a saka tutar ISIS a asibitin.
Ya musanta tuhumar da aka yi masa a karkashin sashe na 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu bayar da shawarwari na kula da lafiyar jama'a, wanda ya goyi bayan Saipow, ya ce sun "yi matukar bakin ciki" bayan hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
Patton ya ce, "Ba hukuncin kisa ba, wanda ba za a iya kawar da shi ba, zai kara wa wadanda suka sha wahala rauni".
Lauyoyin da ke goyon bayan Saipov sun riga sun nemi a dakatar da hukuncin kisa.
