Sabuntawar Red Flu: Ragewar Mahimmanci a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani rahoto na Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa ruwan sama mai ruwan sama a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu.
Hukumar ta ce, an samu karin fure a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier.
Red Falls ya bazu daga arewacin Pinnacle zuwa yankunan Lee na kudu zuwa kusan mil 130 (209,21 km).
